    <briefdescription>
<para>Architecture-specific Stack Walk APIs. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>To add API support to an architecture, <computeroutput><ref refid="group__arch-stackwalk_1ga7129c254277cfa162cd9c5778a7662c2" kindref="member">arch_stack_walk()</ref></computeroutput> should be implemented and a non-user configurable Kconfig <computeroutput>ARCH_HAS_STACKWALK</computeroutput> that is default to <computeroutput>y</computeroutput> should be created in the architecture&apos;s top level Kconfig, with all the relevant dependencies. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
